# в”Җв”Җ P4 blowup DFS л°ңкІ¬ 3кұҙ (D-P4-01~03, 2026-04-14) в”Җв”Җ
@R disc-blowup-p4-qfield-coupling = 0.166667 ratio :: discovery [10]
  "D-P4-01 м–‘мһҗ-мһҘ кІ°н•©мғҒмҲҳ лҸҷм№ҳ: phi*sigma/(n*J2) = 2*12/(6*24) = 24/144 = 1/n = 0.1667. cross-module invariant (quantum.Q2 + field.F4). мҲҳн•ҷм Ғ н•ӯл“ұмӢқмңјлЎң EXACT"
  <- blowup_quantum, blowup_field
  |> experiments/blowup/p4_dfs_5module_report.md
@R disc-blowup-p4-tdual-goldstone-closure = 3.0 divisor :: discovery [10*]
  "D-P4-02 T-duality кіЁл“ңмҠӨнҶӨ м—°мҮ„ нҸҗн•©: (1/phi)*n = n/phi = 6/2 = 3 = divisors(6). лҒҲ T-dual м—ӯмҲҳ+кіЁл“ңмҠӨнҶӨ м—°мҮ„к°Җ 6мқҳ м•ҪмҲҳ кө¬мЎ°м—җ нҸҗн•©. cross-module loop (string.S3 + field.F6). P5 мҠ№кІ©: 3 = 6/2 EXACT мҲҳн•ҷм Ғ н•ӯл“ұмӢқ"
  <- blowup_string, blowup_field
  |> experiments/blowup/p4_dfs_5module_report.md
@R disc-blowup-p4-ouroboros-functor-iso = 1.0 structural :: discovery [9]
  "D-P4-03 мҡ°лЎңліҙлЎңмҠӨ-н•Ёмһҗ лҸҷнҳ•: forge(Saturated) = functor(EXACT->EXACT). MetaLoop мӢңл“ң мһ¬мғқм„ұкіј лІ”мЈјлЎ  л“ұкёүліҙмЎҙмӮ¬мғҒ лҢҖмқ‘. structural isomorphism (ouroboros.MetaLoop + toe.T3). NEAR вҖ” м •лҹү кІҖмҰқ лҢҖкё°"
  <- ouroboros, blowup_toe
  |> experiments/blowup/p4_dfs_5module_report.md
