  <- domains/energy/smr-datacenter/smr-datacenter.md В§X.2
@R SMRDC-07-colocation-loss = L_trans = 1/sigma^2 < 0.7 percent :: n6atlas [10]
  "HEXA-SMR-DC В§X.4: SMR-DC кіөлҸҷмң„м№ҳ мҶЎм „мҶҗмӢӨ. DC bus м§ҒкІ° (AC ліҖнҷҳ 0лӢЁ) вҶ’ 1/ПғВІ=0.69%. grid 6~8% лҢҖл№„ 10л°° к°җмҶҢ. T1 EXACT"
  <- domains/energy/smr-datacenter/smr-datacenter.md В§X.4
