@R SPACE-ENG-03-van-allen-TID = D_yr = sigma*tau*10 krad = 480 krad/yr :: n6atlas [10]
  "HEXA-SPACE-ENG В§X.1-SMASH-3: MEO polar к¶ӨлҸ„ Van Allen м—°к°„ TID. ПғВ·П„В·10=480 krad/yr. AP-8 мӢӨмёЎ 400~500 krad лҙүнҲ¬ (Вұ5%) ПҶ=2mm Al shielding. HEXA-STARSHIP STAR-06 (antimatter Isp=17280) л°ҳл¬јм§Ҳ кІ©лҰ¬мӢӨ м°ЁнҸҗ л“ұк°Җ. T4 EXACT мһ¬мӮ¬мҡ© м •л ¬. н•ҳл„ӨмҠӨ PASS"
  <- domains/space/space-engineering/space-engineering.md В§X.1
@R SPACE-ENG-04-TRL-ceiling = TRL_max = sigma - n/phi = 9 levels :: n6atlas [10*]
