@C kick_bench_smoke_2_line_haiku_poetic_devices_axis_form_compression_name_10 = Form compression: 5-7-5 mora budget reorganized into 2-line structure :: omega_cycle_kick-bench-smoke-2-line-haiku-poetic-devices [7]
