@C kick_bench_smoke_2_line_haiku_poetic_devices_axis_form_compression_rationale_11 = Preserves total syllabic budget and the structural cut; only the line-count surface changes. This option is the only one that retains all three canonical haiku elements (kireji + kigo + juxtaposition)вҖҰ :: omega_cycle_kick-bench-smoke-2-line-haiku-poetic-devices [7]
  => rationale of axis axis_form_compression
  |> kick-bench-smoke-2-line-haiku-poetic-devices (auto-ingested Пү-cycle)

@C kick_bench_smoke_2_line_haiku_poetic_devices_axis_falsifier_coverage_name_12 = Falsifier coverage: what disqualifies a candidate as a 2-line haiku :: omega_cycle_kick-bench-smoke-2-line-haiku-poetic-devices [7]
